<paragraph base="SL30357" id="IAS16_76" principles="no"><paranum>76</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="76"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS16_P0272">In accordance with <xref base="F16451721" href="../ias08/IAS08_TOC.dita#IAS08_TOC0001" id="IAS16_X0251">IAS 8</xref> an entity discloses the nature and effect of a change in an accounting estimate that has an effect in the current period or is expected to have an effect in subsequent periods. For <xref base="SL144217" href="IAS16_6.dita#IAS16_6/IAS16_P0040">property, plant and equipment<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0304"/></ph></xref>, such disclosure may arise from changes in estimates with respect to: </p><ol base="SL144386" id="IAS16_L0026" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="SL144388" id="IAS16_P0273"><xref base="SL144224" href="IAS16_6.dita#IAS16_6/IAS16_P0046">residual values<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0335"/></ph></xref>;</p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="SL144390" id="IAS16_P0274">the estimated costs of dismantling, removing or restoring items of property, plant and equipment;                    </p>       </li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p base="SL144392" id="IAS16_P0275"><xref base="SL144225" href="IAS16_6.dita#IAS16_6/IAS16_P0049">useful lives<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0380"/></ph></xref>; and</p>       </li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value>         <p base="SL144394" id="IAS16_P0276"><xref base="SL144213" href="IAS16_6.dita#IAS16_6/IAS16_P0036">depreciation<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0084"/></ph></xref> methods.                    </p>       </li></ol></body></paragraph>